  "_narrative": "**Where We Stand**\nWe're tied at 0 points with everyone else in Pool C as tournament play begins. Rankings suggest we match up well against most teams in our pool, but anything can happen in tournament hockey.\n\n**Our Next Game**\nWe face the Ennismore Eagles on Friday April 10th at 9:15 AM. On paper we have an edge with our #18 ranking versus their #25, but they'll come out hungry and every team at Provincials earned their spot.\n\n**Around the Pool**\nAlso at 9:15 AM, #3 Kincardine takes on #41 Windsor in what looks like a mismatch on paper. Later at 3:45 PM, we'll face Windsor while Ennismore battles the tournament-favorite Kinucks. We win the pool in 156 out of 729 scenarios, showing there are clear paths forward with strong play.",
